{"tid":275702,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[有圖]有冇人都有眼瞼下垂問題？點解決？","createTime":"2017-06-08T08:47:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-08T12:55:56.000Z","uid":30707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cb091e382ef566c83c88a50b61183b9633a7903f","tid":275702,"uid":30707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T08:47:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做左廿鳩幾年人先發現自己真係有眼瞼下垂問題<br />\n以前都發現自己影相個陣對眼好冇神<br />\n人地影相隻眼係咁<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/08/164454_35dd9b255edf2fed8db35f3da7bc5067.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F08%2F164454_35dd9b255edf2fed8db35f3da7bc5067.jpg&h=8d7c90ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我影相呢就咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/08/164552_90e12253ec65caf01a3ceb5ecfcd52a6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F08%2F164552_90e12253ec65caf01a3ceb5ecfcd52a6.jpg&h=38f46c3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n眼珠得3份2係睇到，上眼皮遮左3份1<br />\n<br />\n最近影相開始試下瞪大d對眼影<br />\n出黎先見到係人地正常影相個樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁無理由成撚日都瞪大對眼架嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我想知有冇巴絲都係咁樣？<br />\n係咪要做手術先解決到？咁樣整一整要幾錢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c7c6f8d6d6bacf08a8f4d5e8d02269e85288cd3","tid":275702,"uid":30707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T08:50:25.000Z","msg":"喊出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e13f740f95fb49ef518ab0e69c7859c1b9b1f866","tid":275702,"uid":48610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T08:53:05.000Z","msg":"我都係<br />\n成日比人問係咪好眼瞓"},{"pid":"d706725382d3ea665e912254328355b909840454","tid":275702,"uid":50491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T08:54:13.000Z","msg":"用得電腦多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e74c0d82c6fe94618881c3342b23371286df1005","tid":275702,"uid":3161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T08:54:39.000Z","msg":"眼臉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 眼簾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8765bb23be1cd6e1087251f340f1981594e7f6e7","tid":275702,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T08:55:22.000Z","msg":"單眼皮真係好樣衰<br />\n關咩事<br />\n提眼肌乏力<br />\n人生已完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd80e00f79073b4e340d69c6acc95fa697c40ac5","tid":275702,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T08:56:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我都係咁<br />\n乜要解決架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幾好喎，攞正牌死魚眼"},{"pid":"83bc765096064be5d13d9fc92ac1cfcb23cfe6c7","tid":275702,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T08:57:13.000Z","msg":"咁樣整同整容有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19312ec80228dbe2d9d0f7638056e4f9e42bfb41","tid":275702,"uid":27097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T08:58:06.000Z","msg":"成日畀人笑死魚眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n畀人話我似劉以達<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7eb7a5dbc6b7518478ced747bcaa3caa89068da5","tid":275702,"uid":30707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T08:59:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>眼臉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 眼簾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n眼瞼先岩"},{"pid":"28db19a5d8909aad85c7044c053681af9e6c0b09","tid":275702,"uid":30707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T08:59:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我都係咁<br />\n乜要解決架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幾好喎，攞正牌死魚眼</blockquote><br />\n要解決架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n勁樣衰，重點係自拍同照鏡個陣睇唔出，但一俾人影相就⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfe3fe4746c10327864f090ade6bf64eea06a585","tid":275702,"uid":30707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T09:00:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁樣整同整容有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我試網睇見有人係因為眼瞼下垂而影響到視力<br />\n重肌無力都有可能"},{"pid":"c215b3880432f9782055913d07adb635e71ce17f","tid":275702,"uid":100016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T09:01:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/08/170119_133883de69ad027d3a8f5653b11b7d58.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F08%2F170119_133883de69ad027d3a8f5653b11b7d58.jpg&h=3199f5a2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"107bec6c8d530bd4726ab3c5ccecf78134ecee8a","tid":275702,"uid":30707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T09:04:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>單眼皮真係好樣衰<br />\n關咩事<br />\n提眼肌乏力<br />\n人生已完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n做手術得架嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最慘我係雙眼皮，更加覺得我個樣似未訓醒<br />\n我之前睇恐怖醫學，有集講到重肌無力可以自我測試<br />\n個人企係到，兩隻手向前伸直，兩隻手要高度一樣，然後合埋眼<br />\n重肌無力嘅人會有一隻手（如果兩邊都重肌無力就兩隻啦）會慢慢垂低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我自己測試過，應該唔係重肌無力"},{"pid":"6a478881636ec49a43a10d62c2fbb6ae9bab2d1d","tid":275702,"uid":30707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T09:05:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/08/170119_133883de69ad027d3a8f5653b11b7d58.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F08%2F170119_133883de69ad027d3a8f5653b11b7d58.jpg&h=3199f5a2&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n我唔係單邊，我係兩隻都係咁<br />\n而且係眼皮擋左三分一眼珠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只有瞪大眼個陣係正常樣"},{"pid":"0676d9e03696e9fb1473964f24528267f7711ff9","tid":275702,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T09:05:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我都係咁<br />\n乜要解決架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幾好喎，攞正牌死魚眼</blockquote><br />\n要解決架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n勁樣衰，重點係自拍同照鏡個陣睇唔出，但一俾人影相就⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n對住鏡練多啲，起碼影相嗰陣冇咁覺先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75a50a6550f45f9f2e85abc587b9fa4bf0d3891e","tid":275702,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T09:06:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成日畀人笑死魚眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n畀人話我似劉以達<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁又慘啲"},{"pid":"3d6d3b5e0308083c7c434b7529e7990d8d1b96d1","tid":275702,"uid":30707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T09:06:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都係<br />\n成日比人問係咪好眼瞓</blockquote><br />\n我試過俾人影返我同人傾計個樣<br />\n我先留意到自己對眼原來一路只係開左一半<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我明明係正常咁睜開眼"},{"pid":"58ea700604ca5aa53b799e30d1a332270a42cd5a","tid":275702,"uid":30707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T09:07:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我都係咁<br />\n乜要解決架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幾好喎，攞正牌死魚眼</blockquote><br />\n要解決架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n勁樣衰，重點係自拍同照鏡個陣睇唔出，但一俾人影相就⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n對住鏡練多啲，起碼影相嗰陣冇咁覺先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n對住鏡/自拍個陣唔洗瞪大眼都係正常<br />\n但係俾人影相個陣先係咁⋯<br />\n所以我都唔知自己係本身習慣唔好定係先天問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4877fe870423e5716bcbe3811fb0a44cdcc1453e","tid":275702,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T09:09:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/1755000/1758585/lycn20170329008_1024_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1755000%2F1758585%2Flycn20170329008_1024_1024.jpg&h=53cff151&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b14ef0f4981f7baee9ccc3bfbf82f117df9c6719","tid":275702,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T09:10:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我都係咁<br />\n乜要解決架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幾好喎，攞正牌死魚眼</blockquote><br />\n要解決架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n勁樣衰，重點係自拍同照鏡個陣睇唔出，但一俾人影相就⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n對住鏡練多啲，起碼影相嗰陣冇咁覺先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n對住鏡/自拍個陣唔洗瞪大眼都係正常<br />\n但係俾人影相個陣先係咁⋯<br />\n所以我都唔知自己係本身習慣唔好定係先天問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所以咪要你練多啲記住個感覺囉<br />\n你自拍/照鏡，自己睇住嚟調整吖嘛<br />\n你唔練多啲咪永遠俾人影都係咁囉"},{"pid":"697293a0f52b03e393bf60eb87ad3ec2d0388cbc","tid":275702,"uid":30707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T09:11:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/1755000/1758585/lycn20170329008_1024_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1755000%2F1758585%2Flycn20170329008_1024_1024.jpg&h=53cff151&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 差唔多啦，我雙眼皮再厚d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd2366e112b60bdeaa4a67ce9c57a123506805a1","tid":275702,"uid":58140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T09:12:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/08/170119_133883de69ad027d3a8f5653b11b7d58.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F08%2F170119_133883de69ad027d3a8f5653b11b7d58.jpg&h=3199f5a2&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n我同呢張差唔多 <br />\n不過無咁誇張<br />\n由細到大都有大細眼問題"},{"pid":"9c69f77a3d3daa37a38c53e27d0bb7be5226c0c3","tid":275702,"uid":30707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T09:14:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我都係咁<br />\n乜要解決架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幾好喎，攞正牌死魚眼</blockquote><br />\n要解決架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n勁樣衰，重點係自拍同照鏡個陣睇唔出，但一俾人影相就⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n對住鏡練多啲，起碼影相嗰陣冇咁覺先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n對住鏡/自拍個陣唔洗瞪大眼都係正常<br />\n但係俾人影相個陣先係咁⋯<br />\n所以我都唔知自己係本身習慣唔好定係先天問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所以咪要你練多啲記住個感覺囉<br />\n你自拍/照鏡，自己睇住嚟調整吖嘛<br />\n你唔練多啲咪永遠俾人影都係咁囉</blockquote><br />\n可能我講得唔好，我係自拍/照鏡個陣只係同平時一樣睜開眼（唔洗用力瞪大）已經係正常樣<br />\n但係俾人影個陣，同樣都係正常睜開眼，對眼出黎就得返一半<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我依家影相係咪都會用力瞪大眼架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但最近俾人話我同人講野個陣對眼好無神<br />\n因為我份工要對客，我覺得呢樣野好緊要<br />\n但我又好難全日都用力瞪大眼，好撚攰<br />\n所以我想知有冇人都係因為呢樣野而去左做手術<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb7e0a8f508f3738d620163cd31459721d425723","tid":275702,"uid":55870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T09:15:43.000Z","msg":"重肌無力症，chec下"}]}